        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer4069051422" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2743919385294237931">Well translated book that demonstrates the violence of the early Christian church that in turn reflects modern religious violence. It is tender as well in describing the conflicts of a monk who wants to be pious but sees the politics in religion.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


